**File:** `packages/design-system/tokens/README.md`

````markdown
# Lufa Design System v2.0 - Primitive Tokens

**Level:** 1 (Primitives)  
**Status:** ✅ Complete (97 tokens)  
**Package:** `@grasdouble/lufa_design-system-tokens`

## Overview

Primitive tokens are the foundation of Lufa Design System v2.0. They define raw, non-semantic values that serve as building blocks for higher-level tokens (Core, Semantic, Component).

**Total Tokens:** 97

| Category      | Count | Description                          |
| ------------- | ----- | ------------------------------------ |
| Colors        | 54    | 6 colors × 9 shades (Tailwind-style) |
| Font Families | 2     | Sans-serif and monospace stacks      |
| Spacing       | 12    | 4px-based scale (0-96px)             |
| Font Sizes    | 9     | xs (12px) to 5xl (48px)              |
| Font Weights  | 4     | Normal to Bold (400-700)             |
| Line Heights  | 3     | Tight, Normal, Relaxed (1.25-1.75)   |
| Shadows       | 6     | None to XL (5 elevation levels)      |
| Border Radii  | 7     | None to Full (0-9999px)              |

## Installation

```bash
pnpm add @grasdouble/lufa_design-system-tokens
```
````

## Usage

### CSS (Recommended)

```css
@import '@grasdouble/lufa_design-system-tokens/dist/tokens.css';

.button {
  padding: var(--lufa-primitive-spacing-8) var(--lufa-primitive-spacing-16);
  font-size: var(--lufa-primitive-typography-font-size-base);
  font-weight: var(--lufa-primitive-typography-font-weight-semibold);
  border-radius: var(--lufa-primitive-radius-base);
  background-color: var(--lufa-primitive-color-blue-500);
  color: var(--lufa-primitive-color-gray-50);
  box-shadow: var(--lufa-primitive-shadow-sm);
}
```

### TypeScript/JavaScript

```typescript
import tokens from '@grasdouble/lufa_design-system-tokens/dist/tokens';

const buttonStyles = {
  padding: `${tokens.primitive.spacing[8]} ${tokens.primitive.spacing[16]}`,
  fontSize: tokens.primitive.typography.fontSize.base,
  fontWeight: tokens.primitive.typography.fontWeight.semibold,
  borderRadius: tokens.primitive.radius.base,
  backgroundColor: tokens.primitive.color.blue[500],
  color: tokens.primitive.color.gray[50],
  boxShadow: tokens.primitive.shadow.sm,
};
```

## Token Structure

All tokens follow the DTCG format with metadata:

```json
{
  "$value": "16px",
  "$type": "dimension",
  "$description": "Base spacing - standard component gaps",
  "metadata": {
    "level": "primitive",
    "category": "spacing",
    "useCase": "section margins, component spacing"
  }
}
```

## Color Palette

**Gray** - Neutral backgrounds, text, borders  
**Blue** - Primary brand, links, info states  
**Red** - Error states, destructive actions  
**Green** - Success states, positive feedback  
**Yellow** - Warning states, caution  
**Purple** - Secondary brand, accent

Each color has 9 shades (50, 100, 200, 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 900) with WCAG AA compliance metadata.

## Spacing Scale (4px base)

```
0px, 4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 24px, 32px, 40px, 48px, 64px, 80px, 96px
```

## Typography

**Font Families:**

- Sans: System font stack (system-ui, -apple-system, etc.) - 0kb download
- Mono: Monospace stack (ui-monospace, SF Mono, etc.) - 0kb download

**Font Sizes:**

- xs (12px), sm (14px), base (16px), lg (18px), xl (20px)
- 2xl (24px), 3xl (30px), 4xl (36px), 5xl (48px)

**Font Weights:**

- Normal (400), Medium (500), Semibold (600), Bold (700)

**Line Heights:**

- Tight (1.25), Normal (1.5), Relaxed (1.75)

## Shadows

6 elevation levels (none, sm, base, md, lg, xl) with progressively larger blur and darker opacity.

## Border Radii

7 values: none (0px), sm (2px), base (4px), md (6px), lg (8px), xl (12px), full (9999px)

## Development

```bash
# Build tokens
pnpm build

# Watch mode
pnpm build:watch

# Validate metadata
pnpm validate
```

## Architecture

Primitive tokens are **Level 1** in the 4-level token architecture:

1. **Primitives** (this package) - Raw values
2. **Core Tokens** (coming in Semaine 2) - Basic semantic mappings
3. **Semantic Tokens** (coming in Semaine 3) - Context-specific tokens
4. **Component Tokens** (coming in Phases 2-3) - Component-specific overrides

## Performance

- **Bundle Size:** ~8KB (CSS) + ~6KB (TypeScript)
- **Build Time:** <1s (97 tokens)
- **Zero Runtime Cost:** All tokens are compile-time constants

